#org @arianaTalk
= No, Giovanni!\c\h08ó\nPlease, don't go!\c\h08ó I won't allow this to happen!

#org @bossTalk
= [.]\c\h08óThere's nothing you can say,\ndarling.\lLeave me be.

#org @bossTalk2
= Giovanni: [player].\c\h08ó\nYou're here at last.\pI'm ashamed you should have to see\nme like this[.]

#org @bossTalk3
= I've been defeated in battle for\nthe very last time.\pI cannot face my followers any\nlonger.\pI've[.]\c\h08ó betrayed your trust.

#org @bossTalk4
= With the last bit of scrap of honor I\nhave left[.]\pIt's time for me to move on.\pWe've worn out our welcome in\nKanto long ago.\pI think it's best[.]\c\h08ó if this were\nthe end of Team Rocket.

#org @bossTalk5
= [.]\pBut I don't expect all of my\nAdmins and Executives to agree.


#org @bossTalk6
= So, [player][.]\pYou are free to keep wreaking\nhavoc on Kanto if you prefer.\pBut whatever becomes of Team\nRocket from here on out[.]\pIt will be without me at the helm.

#org @arianaTalk2
= Ariana: I-I[.]\c\h08ó\nI won't have this insanity!\pA-all our work, Giovanni!\nEverything we stood for..!\pOver some child..?

#org @bossTalk7
= Giovanni: Yes, a child, Ariana.\c\h08ó\nA child who will soon rule the\lregion[.]\pWithout the slightest bloodshed\nto his name.\pAnd what have we achieved?

#org @bossTalk8
= We've roused the anger and the\nsupport of those who longed back\lto the golden years of Kanto[.]\pAnd become the masters of its\ncriminal underworld.\pBut we're no closer to our ultimate\ngoal than we were ten years ago[.]

#org @bossTalk9
= I truly thought we had the clearest\npath to power laid out for us[.]\p[.]\pI was lying to myself the whole\ntime.

#org @bossTalk10
= That kid[.]\pFrom the first I ever heard of him,\nhe made me so[.]\c\h08ó\angry[.]\pAll my violent frustration, my\nbitterness[.]\pI didn't understand why he brought\nit all out of me[.]\pDidn't understand that he was\nmaking me see, all too clearly[.]\pThe blind, stubborn weakling I had\nbecome.

#org @bossTalk11
= But I do now.\c\h08ó\nAnd so it's time for me to go.

#org @bossTalk12
= [player].\c\h08ó\nI apologize for everything.\pTeam Rocket will not rule Kanto.

#org @bossTalk13
= I guess you can say this could be the end[.]\But it won't be for you.

#org @bossTalk14
= So, take this.\pAs a final token of my\nappreciation, [player].

#org @bossTalk15
= I had such high hopes for you.\c\h08ó\nIt makes me proud[.]\pHow far you've come since I first\ncalled you into my office all that\ltime ago[.]

#org @bossTalk16
= Make the best of the power and\nresponsibility I've given you.\pSo long.

#org @silverTalk1
= No!\c\h08ó\nCome back, you bastard..!

#org @silverTalk2
= Silver: Don't you dare[.]\c\h08ó\nDon't you dare run away!\pI hate you!\pYou're the reason for everything\nthat's bad!\

#org @arianaTalk3
= Ariana: [.]\c\h08ó\n(Be strong[.])\p(It's what he would have wanted[.])


